<html>
<body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:1.38;margin:0;padding:0;">
<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Hi [applicant_first_name],</strong></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">We are pleased to inform you that you have been selected for the <strong style="font-weight:700">[job_title]</strong> role at <strong style="font-weight:700">Outsourced Pro Global</strong>.</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">As the next step, we would like to invite you for a <strong style="font-weight:700">job offer discussion</strong>. During this discussion, we will:</span></span></p>

<ol style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.38;color:#000000;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;padding-left:22px;">
<li style="margin-bottom:10px;">Go through your <strong style="font-weight:700">job offer letter</strong>, including your professional service fees, benefits, and requirements ahead of your onboarding date.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:10px;">Conduct a <strong style="font-weight:700">system check</strong> of your working device to ensure it meets our required standards.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:10px;">Submit <strong style="font-weight:700">2 valid government IDs</strong> (front and back) on the same day.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:10px;">Prepare <strong style="font-weight:700">3 character references</strong> along with their availability for a verification call.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:10px;">Send your <strong style="font-weight:700">NBI/PCC clearance</strong>, ensuring it has at least 6 months of validity remaining. If it is not yet available, send an <strong style="font-weight:700">appointment receipt</strong> instead.</li>
</ol>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Interview details:</strong></span></span></p>
<div style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:#000000;margin:0 0 16px 0;padding:14px 16px;background-color:#f5f5f5;border-left:3px solid #cccccc;">
<strong style="font-weight:700">Date:</strong> [Date]<br>
<strong style="font-weight:700">Time:</strong> [Time] [Timezone]<br>
<strong style="font-weight:700">Platform:</strong> Zoom<br>
<strong style="font-weight:700">Zoom Link:</strong> <a href="[Link]" style="color:#1155cc;text-decoration:underline">[Link]</a>
</div>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Friendly Reminders:</strong></span></span></p>

<ul style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.38;color:#000000;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;padding-left:22px;">
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;">Kindly <strong style="font-weight:700">connect 10 minutes early</strong> to make sure your camera and microphone are working properly.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;">Use your laptop or PC for this interview.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;">Make sure that your <strong style="font-weight:700">Full Name</strong> and the <strong style="font-weight:700">role</strong> you are interviewing for are reflected in the Zoom meeting.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;">Please note that this is a formal meeting - please dress in business attire.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;">If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to any of our recruiters at <strong style="font-weight:700">+61 489 275 966 (AU)</strong> or <strong style="font-weight:700">[recruiter_phone_line]</strong>.</li>
</ul>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:4px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Warm regards,</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Recruitment Team, Outsourced Pro Global</strong></span></span></p>

[signature]
</body>
</html>
